import * as React from 'react';

                  Field Buddy
                </Text>

            </Flex>
          </Box>

};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    backgroundColor: "#F0F4FF",
    flex: 1,
    height: "100%",
    alignItems: "center",
    padding: "1em",

  box: {
    borderRadius: 10,

    width: "30%",
  },
  boxHeader: {
    color: "#ADB3D2",
    fontSize: "1.5em",

export default FifthPage;
